{"tid":96040,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"狗會真係好狗","createTime":"2017-01-26T13:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T05:16:10.000Z","uid":717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6116999d16312f1cf8b8858897d3bb168a56d80a","tid":96040,"uid":717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"六合彩以往累積獎金係一定會等到有人中先到下一個彩池，結果今日去買頭獎得2200萬，咁差額既5800萬去左邊？ <br />\n<br />\n經過一番思考之後，我上網再望下，佢auntie 啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狗會特別加左個初一新年金多寶同3T 合共8000萬同1億，好巧妙地轉移左失蹤既5800萬既視線去新年金多寶同3T，你可能會覺得好好，又有2200萬又8000萬又三T <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但你有無諗到原本應該係8000萬加8000萬加三T<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n最終個5800萬去左邊，相信唔洗我多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我再強調多次，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">六合彩以往累積獎金係一定會等到有人中先到下一個彩池</span><br />\n<br />\n我知我都係唔會中，但每一個香港人都係想買個希望姐，邊個唔係啊:(<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t30r00N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft30r00N.jpg&h=d47c4664&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c7284757b5fca229dc70bfd20f7598e79875cab","tid":96040,"uid":25656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:31:27.000Z","msg":"你驗咗眼先"},{"pid":"403c107fa4ed0fc76d9897a938d0968d6c59297b","tid":96040,"uid":49064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:32:23.000Z","msg":"5千萬咪派晒俾你地囉"},{"pid":"5ae74943f37fb1b4cfc86240965f4f176d7f676b","tid":96040,"uid":28736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:40:52.000Z","msg":"留明睇樓主柒"},{"pid":"a232083a50a59a09b033216f7af945c8e0216078","tid":96040,"uid":39439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T04:47:07.000Z","msg":"Ching講得好"},{"pid":"aa0fcbd1b1b67784f16aee35519d18ed59ee3f6c","tid":96040,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}